div.head:
{@sāraḷā mahābhārata
udyoga paba
gaṇeśaṅka bandanā@}

{@pāṇḍabaṅka indraprasthe prabeśa, dhr̥tarāṣṭra sañjaẏa saṁbāda
o dhaumya purohitaṅkara dūtapaṇe
hastinā gamana@}

lg.head:
{@uttarā bāḷīra rajobatī hebā sambāda
o
rajakoṣṭha bibaraṇa@}

div.head:
{@pañcha pāṇḍabaṁkara samara pratiygāṁ, dūtapaṇe
śrīkr̥ṣṇaṅkara hastinā gamana o byāsādi
muniṅka saha bidura gr̥he biśrāma@}

lg.head:
{@śrīkr̥ṣṇaṅkara bidura mandirare abasthiti
o
biduraṅku bara dāna@}

div.head:
{@kuntī o śrīkr̥ṣṇaṅka kathopakathana, śrīkr̥ṣṇa
dhr̥tarāṣṭaṁka nikaṭe prabeśa ebaṁ andha
brāhmaṇara gakṣudāna bibaraṇa@}

{@śrīkr̥ṣṇaṅkara prathama thara kurusabhāku gamana
ebaṁ
apamāna o baḷirājāra upākhyāna@}

{@duryyodhana duikhaṇḍa paḍā debā nimante
bhīṣmaṅkaṭhāre icchā prakāśa o śakunira
amata ebaṁ bābanā bhūtara bibaraṇa@}

{@kauraba sabhāku śrīkr̥ṣṇaṅkara tr̥tīẏa thara gamana
o
apamāna ebaṁ mahālakṣmī sahita dvāraka gamana@}

lg.head:
{@mahālakṣmīṅku aṇibā nimante duryyodhana śakuniṅka
dvārikā gamana o śrīkr̥ṣṇaṅku āṇibā nimante
arjunaṅkara dvārikā yātrā@}

{@śrīkr̥ṣṇaṅkara indraprasthe āgamana,
kurukṣetra baṇṭana nimante śakunira yudhiṣṭhiraṅka
nikaṭe prabeśa o aḷasuā bibaraṇa@}

div.head:
{@kurukṣetrare śubhastambha sthāpana, tahiṁ madhyaṁstha
puruṣa ebaṁ pūrṇṇa praḷaẏa o debanāśana
baṭa prabhr̥tira bibaraṇa@}

lg.head:
{@kuru pāṇḍabaṅkara sanya saṁkhyā
śrīkr̥ṣṇaṅka dvārā belāḷasena mastaka cchedana o
śubhastambha sthāpana ebaṁ pāṇḍabamānaṅka channatā@}

div.head:
{@karṇṇaku āṇibā kimante kuntīṅkara gamana ebaṁ
nīḷabāṇa bhr̥jabāṇa dakṣiṇā svarūpe
ānaẏana@}
